# [[Thanksgiving Weekend]] or [[Black Friday Weekend]] {{gloss|the shopping period from [[Thanksgiving Thursday]] (U.S. [[Thanksgiving Day]]) through [[Cyber Monday]] ({{m|fr|cyberlundi}}), including [[Black Friday]] ({{m|fr|vendredi noir}} or {{m|fr|vendredi fou}}), with large discounts in the prices of goods}}

====Usage notes====
Though the holiday period is exclusive to the United States of America, the marketing and sales event has expanded out through the English-speaking world, and also into Europe. The holiday has not followed the sales and marketing event into other nations.

